{"tid":722301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日面試比人性騷擾","createTime":"2018-06-29T11:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T11:21:46.000Z","uid":128057,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb465aa4d7990967f9011a31136623b394b9032","tid":722301,"uid":128057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我in嘅位係秘書<br />\n所以直接由老闆interview<br />\n一開始in個陣都好正常<br />\n但係講完啲面試內容之後<br />\n佢話倒杯水比我飲 傾到口乾<br />\n之後拎過黎既時候唔小心倒杯水落我心口到<br />\n唔知佢有意定冇意<br />\n但之後佢就扮好心拎紙巾抺我個胸<br />\n我反應唔切 比佢禁左我個胸幾下<br />\n事後諗返 覺得佢性騷擾我<br />\n而家人又走左<br />\n我又冇證據<br />\n點樣可以告佢？"},{"pid":"0b38f22ee8aef02277d4fb48dedc2b3c17ebb23b","tid":722301,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fa019059bf599a074506f05e34ec635838f3242","tid":722301,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"你咩cup先？"},{"pid":"ea5d6759852b939894779fb1d3e33dba36375057","tid":722301,"uid":24675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faecc64c99c772e63d36f58edb0cae161c511b54","tid":722301,"uid":166792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:18:55.000Z","msg":"男人之家大方d啦"},{"pid":"9fb2fccd24f3e59a66a3e6a7324e432c50435d89","tid":722301,"uid":96,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"有冇摸埋你條J"},{"pid":"d4a794f7096e4c29de5f1df8fcaba26be1450c6f","tid":722301,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"起底》負評〉上一頁"},{"pid":"cd1db847fc23da49e15d78f1532292f6b63d2a23","tid":722301,"uid":123456,"like